OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,FITV News reporter Emma Sweeney spoke
OL,7,Fto Daisy Martin, whose ex-partner has
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty of coercive control.
OL,10,FA woman who was subjected to
OL,11,Fcontrolling and coercive behaviour by
OL,12,Fher ex-partner says her "sense of
OL,13,Fsafety is gone".
OL,15,FDuring the course of their
OL,16,Frelationship Callum Coady, from
OL,17,FStockport, insulted and belittled his
OL,18,Fthen girlfriend, Daisy Martin who was
OL,19,Fjust 20 at the time, bombarding her
OL,20,Fwith thousands of messages.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
