OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,FHe was arrested on 19 August 2023 at
OL,7,FManchester Airport, after staff
OL,8,Fintervened as he threw a glass of
OL,9,Fprosecco in her face.
OL,11,FDaisy said: "All I remember was my
OL,12,Feyes stinging and feeling absolutely
OL,13,Fwet through and that's when I knew
OL,14,Fhe'd threw the prosecco on me.
OL,16,F"I remember thinking he's going to hit
OL,17,Fme. I just jumped up and jumped back."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773760268
OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,FFollowing the arrest, Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police's Domestic Abuse
OL,8,FTeam in Stockport went through more
OL,9,Fthan 35,000 messages to uncover "a
OL,10,Fclear and persistent pattern of
OL,11,Fcontrol, threats, and manipulation".
OL,13,FDaisy, who has waived her right to
OL,14,Fanonymity to speak out about the
OL,15,Fabuse, said she has been left
OL,16,Fconstantly looking over her shoulder.
OL,18,F"He made me delete social media just
OL,19,Fbecause I had other male friends on
OL,20,Fthere. He didn't like me posting
OL,21,Fmyself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773760268
OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,F"He'd insult me, he'd call me names.
OL,7,FIf I wasn't replying he'd video who I
OL,8,Fwas with, ask me to prove to him where
OL,9,FI was. If I didn't it would be a phone
OL,10,Fcall or 'I'm coming, I'm coming now'
OL,12,F"After that it would be him being
OL,13,Funder the influence, being back at his
OL,14,Fhouse and him screaming at me for
OL,15,Fsomething I don't know what, but even
OL,16,Fhis mum would come in and say that's
OL,17,Fenough and I'd have to tell her it's
OL,18,Ffine."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
