OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,FCoady, of Larwood Avenue, Heaton
OL,7,FMersey, pleaded guilty to coercive
OL,8,Fcontrol and was sentenced to 16 weeks
OL,9,Fin prison, suspended for 12 months, at
OL,10,FManchester Magistrates' Court on
OL,11,FMonday 16 March 2026.
OL,13,FThe 27-year-old was also handed a five-
OL,14,Fyear restraining order and made to pay
OL,15,FDaisy #200 in compensation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
