CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773760268
OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,FThe court heard the Domestic Abuse
OL,7,FTeam's investigation found Coady had
OL,8,Fbecome increasingly aggressive and
OL,9,Fcontrolling throughout the
OL,10,Frelationship, forcing Daisy to delete
OL,11,Fher social media, monitoring her
OL,12,Fonline activity, dictated what she
OL,13,Fwore, and restricting contact with
OL,14,Ffriends and family.
OL,16,FOne text chain from Coady read: "Why
OL,17,Fhave you turned your read receipts off
OL,18,Fturn it back on NOW".
OL,20,FIt continued: "Who are you talking to.
OL,21,FBlock him
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773760268
OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,F"Turn them on now B****. Sorry I love
OL,7,Fyou. I love you. Just do it NOW"
OL,9,FDaisy said: "He made me feel unlovable
OL,10,Fand affected my self-confidence. I
OL,11,Foverthink everything and notice
OL,12,Fchanges in myself - getting angry more
OL,13,Feasily and snapping. I'm trying to
OL,14,Frebuild myself.
OL,16,F"I blamed myself for not seeing the
OL,17,Fmanipulation sooner.
OL,19,F"Now small things trigger doubt, and
OL,20,Fif someone seems distant, I assume
OL,21,FI've done something wrong.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773760268
OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,F"I used to be open and secure, but
OL,7,Fthat part of me feels damaged. This
OL,8,Fexperience has deeply affected my
OL,9,Ftrust and identity."
OL,11,FDetective Constable Elizabeth Andrews
OL,12,Fsaid: "Daisy has shown exceptional
OL,13,Fbravery throughout this case.
OL,15,F"Her strength in coming forward, her
OL,16,Fhonesty, and her continued co-
OL,17,Foperation with our officers has been
OL,18,Fvital in securing today's sentence.
OL,26,@qD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773760268
OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,F"The thousands of messages recovered
OL,7,Ffrom Coady's phone provided a clear
OL,8,Fand disturbing insight into the level
OL,9,Fof control, manipulation and abuse she
OL,10,Fwas subjected to, and they formed a
OL,11,Fcrucial part of the evidence against
OL,12,Fhim.
OL,14,F"It is important for people to know
OL,15,Fthat coercive and controlling
OL,16,Fbehaviour is a crime, and it will
OL,17,Fnever be tolerated.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
