PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773760268
OL,3,C'He made me forget what love should
OL,4,Cfeel like': Woman sees abuser sentenced
OL,6,F"If you are experiencing anything like
OL,7,Fthis, please report it. You will be
OL,8,Flistened to, you will be believed, and
OL,9,Fwe will do everything we can to
OL,10,Fprotect you and bring offenders to
OL,11,Fjustice."
OL,13,FTo help people spot the warning signs
OL,14,Fof coercive and controlling behaviour,
OL,15,Fthe Mayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,16,FBurnham, has launched the _IsThisOkay
OL,17,Fcampaign.
OL,19,FMore information and support can be
OL,20,Ffound here.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
